                                                    1996
                                                </span>
                                                <!--<span class="timeline-date">11:35 am</span> -->
                                                <h1 class="text-uppercase">Bigger and semi automatic Shell Molding foundry (PLANT II) was officially Inaugurated.</h1>
                                                <p class="clr_ff">Obtained the ISO 9002 Certification from RWTUV, Germany</p>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </article>
