                                            <div class="panel-body">
                                                <span class="timeline-icon">
                                                    2001
                                                </span>
                                                
                                                <h1 class="text-uppercase">With an objective to add value the castings manufactured, a complete machining facility PLANT III was inaugurated. </h1>
                                                <!--<p class="clr_ff">Obtained the ISO 9002 Certification from RWTUV, Germany</p>
                                                <p class="clr_ff">Received the “Best Foundry” award</p> -->
                                               
