         <div id="visionpolicy" class="page-content quality"  name="visionpolicy">
        		<div class="heading-title text-center">
                	<h1 class="text-uppercase text-center m-bot-40">Vision and Policies</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                        	<h3 class="text-uppercase" style="margin-bottom:10px">Vision</h3>
                        	<p>
                            	It is the vision of INDOSHELL MOULD LIMITED to be a WORLD CLASS ORGANIZATION in all respects.  
                            </p>
                            <p>This vision will be met by,</p>
                            <ul class="listyle">
                            <li>Attaining Market leadership by exceeding Customer expectations and outperforming competitors in
Quality, Delivery and Cost.</li>
                            <li>By our ongoing commitment to Continual Improvement of our Products, Processes and Service.</li>
                            <li>By total employee involvement, obtained through education and training for continuous growth.</li>
                            <li>To be a premier Supplier to our Customers while holding the highest regard for our People, Community
and Environment.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h3 class="text-uppercase m-bot-15 m-top-15" style="margin-bottom:10px">Six Sigma</h3>
                            <p style="margin-bottom:40px">
                            	To solve the Quality problems in a scientific way Indo Shell developed 5 Six Sigma Black Belt Holders. To achieve Rejection reduction Process variation reduction various projects are identified on a continuous basis and problems are solved. 
                            </p> 

                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <!-- accordion 2 start-->
                            <dl class="accordion" style="margin-bottom:40px;">
                                <dt>
                                    <a href="">Quality Policy</a>
                                </dt>
                                <dd>
                                                        
                                    <p>It is the Vision of IndoShell Mould Limited to be a WORLD CLASS ORGANIZATION in Manufacturing of Castings, Machined Components and Sub-assemblies
                                    <br>
                                    This Vision will be met by,
                                     </p>
                                       
                                    <ul class="listyle">
                                        <li>Attaining Market leadership by exceeding customer expectations and outperforming competitors in Quality, Delivery and Cost.</li>
                                        <li>By our ongoing commitment to Continual Improvement of our Products, Processes and Service. </li>
                                        <li>By total employee involvement, obtained through education and training for continuous growth.</li>
                                        <li>To be a premier Supplier to our Customers while holding the highest regard for our Employees and other interested parties such as Suppliers.</li>
                                        <li>Complying with all applicable customer specific requirements, statutory and regulatory requirements, Product Safety, Product Environmental requirements and Corporate Social Policy requirements.</li>
                                    </ul>

                                    
                                </dd>
                                <dt>
                                    <a href="">Environmental Safety Policy</a>
                                </dt>
                                <dd>
                                	<p>Indo Shell Mould Limited, Leading manufacturer of shell Moulded Castings, is committed to be an environmentally Responsible Organization through,
                                    </p>
                                   
							<ul class="listyle">
                                <li>Adopting Eco-friendly Work Methods and Processes thereby reducing Environmental pollution.</li>
                                <li>Conservation of Natural Resources through Efficient Utilization of Key resources & materials.</li>
                                <li>Reduce,Reuse and Recycle Wastes to the extent possible.</li>
                                <li>Complying with all applicable Legal and Other requirements related to Environment.</li>
                                <li>Monitoring and Continually Improving our Environmental Performance Periodically.</li>
                                <li>Creating Awareness and involving all Employees in our Environment Management System.</li>
                            </ul>
                                    
                                </dd>
                                
                                 <dt>
                                    <a href="">TPM Policy</a>
                                </dt>
                                <dd>
                                
                                
                           <p style="margin-bottom:20px">It is the Vision of Indo Shell Mould Limited to be a World Class Organisation through TPM.
                            This Vision will be met by 
                              </p>
							<ul class="tpmpolicy">
                            <li>Total Customer satisfaction through Highest Quality at lowest Cost and Speed in Delivery</li>
                            <li>Establishing a maintenance system for the entire life of the equipment</li>
                            <li>Maximising the Overall Plant Effectiveness</li>
                            <li>Total employee involvement</li>
                            <li>Continuous improvement towards Zero defect, Zero wastage, Zero breakdown</li>
                            <li>Creating a clean and safe working environment</li>
                          

                            </ul>
                            
                            </dd>
                               
                            </dl>
